{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36314-caterpillar-sokha-koeb","title":"ບົ້ງນ້ອຍຊອກຫາເກີບ","description":"ເກີບບົ້ງນ້ອຍເສຍ ລາວພະຍາຍາມຊອກຢືມເກີບນໍາແມງມູມ, ກົບ, ຕັກກະແຕນ ແລະ ກະປູ ແຕ່ບໍ່ມີເກີບຄູ່ໃດພໍດີຕີນຂອງລາວ. ບົ້ງນ້ອຍຈະເຮັດແນວໃດເມື່ອລາວບໍ່ມີເກີບ?","language":"Lao","langCode":"lo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Somsanouk  Bouttavong"],"illustrators":["Ounla  Santi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36314-caterpillar-sokha-koeb"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93875/size3/0dcaaa20a0eecc067f04048b55ea5c1f.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93875/size6/0dcaaa20a0eecc067f04048b55ea5c1f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70961/size6/b8d053bf6ebb59b059a270e9b9963118.jpg","text":"ເກີບຂອງບົ້ງນ້ອຍເສຍ ລາວຍ່າງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖ້າເກີບຂອງລາວບໍ່ຄົບ.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70962/size6/ca8afe61ccf57f27d5a8ee2cbf109383.jpg","text":"ບົ້ງໄປຂໍຢືມເກີບນໍາແມງມູມ ເກີບຂອງແມງມູມນ້ອຍໂພດ ມັນເອົາໄວ້ທາວໄຍ.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70963/size6/c6cf12978494f05e16201416d353ac23.jpg","text":"ບົ້ງນ້ອຍເສົ້າໃຈເພາະລາວ ບ່ໍມີເກີບຄົບຕີນຂອງລາວ.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70964/size6/6dc6892c3e74cef23ede18e7754d2736.jpg","text":"ບົ້ງນ້ອຍໄປຂໍຢືມເກີບນໍາກົບ.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70965/size6/2db646a85e66982d55e647d73c6cf0c2.jpg","text":"ກົບກໍໃຫ້ຢືມແຕ່ບົ້ງນ້ອຍໃສ່ບໍ່ໄດ້